column5: Mine is; to catch a big Tarpon, fish Arctic Char on the Tree River. Snorkel in a tropical lagoon..
Peacock bass in the amazon, LTW/Eagle Lake/Lac seul musky hunting, catch a pickeral...instead of those pesky walleye
I WANT THE VIRGINS BEFORE I MEET ALLAH!!!!!
Mine's actually very simple... I want to live long enough to retire! HH
I want to live forever. So far so good.
